  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Being bed and breakfast, there is no restaurant onsite at Hotel Internazionale however there is a quaint breakfast room where a continental buffet of hot and cold foods is served each morning. With freshly baked breads, cakes, pastries along with cold cuts, local cheeses, pancakes, bacon and eggs cooked to order there is plenty to get you started for your day. The bar in the hotel is open for an a la carte lunch service which can be booked and paid for locally where you can dine out on the terrace overlooking the lake from a menu of stone baked pizzas, paninis and pasta. The bar is open late into the evening and is the perfect spot for a nightcap when you've returned from dinner at one of the many restaurants located in the centre of Malcesine just 10 minutes away on foot. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
